OL,3,CWoman's dream retirement ruined as
OL,4,Cmesh surgery leaves her in constant
OL,5,Cpain
OL,7,FJosie Ramsden suffered with
OL,8,Fconstipation for years and was
OL,9,Freferred to Mr Dixon and had her first
OL,10,Fconsultation with him in 2009.
OL,12,FShe was told she needed Laparoscopic
OL,13,FVentral Mesh Rectopexy (LVMR) surgery,
OL,14,Fand was referred by the NHS to have
OL,15,Fthe procedure performed at Bristol
OL,16,FSpire Hospital by Mr Dixon.
OL,18,F"I live with pain," she said. "I never
OL,19,Fknow if I'm going to have another
OL,20,Fblockage."
