OL,7,FShe added: "I'm very fortunate that my
OL,8,Fconsultant now has an open appointment
OL,9,Fand I can see her when I need to, and
OL,10,FI do. But that is the rest of my life
OL,11,Fnow, and my husband's life, and my
OL,12,Ffamily's life - they're always
OL,13,Fworried."
