OL,7,FHe said: "I have accepted the findings
OL,8,Fof misconduct made against me by the
OL,9,FMedical Practitioners Tribunal.
OL,11,F"Despite my wrongdoing, my only wish
OL,12,Fwas to make (my patients) better. I
OL,13,Fconsidered that I was acting in my
OL,14,Fpatients' best interests, as the
OL,15,Ftribunal have accepted.
