OL,7,F"I am very sorry and deeply regret the
OL,8,Fmisconduct described by the Tribunal
OL,9,F.... I am committed to learning from
OL,10,Fmy mistakes and to .. regain(ing)
OL,11,Fpeople's trust and to continue working
OL,12,Ftowards becoming once again the
OL,13,Fethical and trustworthy doctor that
OL,14,Fevery patient deserves and one that I
OL,15,Fwas previously recognised for.
OL,17,F"The tribunal has accepted the many
OL,18,Fsupportive testimonials received from
OL,19,Fnumerous patients of mine as well as
OL,20,Fmy former colleagues."
