OL,7,FThe Spire Hospital and North Bristol
OL,8,FNHS Trust declined to comment on
OL,9,Findividual cases.
OL,11,FHowever in a statement a Spire
OL,12,Fspokesperson apologised "to all
OL,13,Fpatients whose care with Mr Dixon fell
OL,14,Fbelow the standards that should have
OL,15,Fbeen provided".
OL,17,FThey added Mr Dixon was suspended in
OL,18,F2017 and has not worked there since,
OL,19,Fsaying: "We also referred Mr Dixon to
OL,20,Fthe GMC and worked closely with the
OL,21,FGMC in its investigations."
