OL,7,FNorth Bristol NHS Trust's Chief
OL,8,FMedical Officer Tim Whittlestone told
OL,9,FITV News Mr Dixon was dismissed in
OL,10,F2019.
OL,12,F"We have carried out a thorough and
OL,13,Frobust review of affected patients,
OL,14,Fand would like to reiterate our
OL,15,Fapology to all of these individuals,"
OL,16,Fhe added.
OL,18,F"We note the outcome of the recent
OL,19,FMPTS hearing."
